comments: Morris (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position on Conley (UTA) off ball and incidental foot to foot contact occurs.
Morris (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Conley (UTA).
Jokic (DEN) makes contact with Gobert's (UTA) arm during his shooting motion that affects his shot near the rim.
Murray (DEN) is standing inside the three-point arc prior to the release of the free throw.
Murray (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Gobert's (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
During the drive, Jokic (DEN) makes contact to Conley's (UTA) body and the contact affects his SQBR.
Bogdanovic (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position on Morris (DEN) off ball as he tries to deflect the pass.
During the drive, Mitchell (UTA) plants his foot and releases from the contact with Harris (DEN).
Conley (UTA) places a forearm against Morris (DEN) during his shot attempt but does not apply any force and the contact is marginal.
During the rebound, Jokic (DEN) jumps for the ball and does not deliver contact to O'Neale (UTA) to dislodge him from his position.
O'Neale (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position during the tip-in attempt by Jokic (DEN).
After the tip shot, Jokic (DEN) returns to the ground and incidental foot to foot contact occurs with Gobert (UTA) that causes Jokic to lose his balance.
Harris (DEN) attempts to steal the ball and marginal contact occurs with Conley's (UTA) body that does not affect his ability to push the ball up court.

Replay review of the foul called on Dozier (DEN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Dozier is in the RA at the time of the contact with O'Neale (UTA) during his driving shot attempt.
Dozier (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in O'Neale's (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
O'Neale (UTA) legally contests Murray's (DEN) jump shot attempt and then contorts his body around Murray to avoid any body follow-through contact.
After the hand-off, Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Favors' (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
